Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:09.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾有互相憎恨之人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍腐於野 血染英魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羈絆斷於利刃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.24,0:00:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心在黑暗中哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.96,0:00:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心愛之人 且赴黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.30,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹小姐 因為我如此肥胖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.88,0:02:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一定要娶你這般細腰的女子才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.56,0:03:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我時常這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.54,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹小姐厭惡肥胖之人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何 我們也學學弦之介大人與朧小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不住口 丈助 真沒酒品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看見朱絹小姐一臉為難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可糟了 像是稍稍喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這真美味 醃得真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與甲賀的相比別有風味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,定是鹽的緣故 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀所購之鹽均產自赤穗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.55,0:03:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是喜歡不妨帶些回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後面鹽倉中還貯有好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.34,0:03:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是有備無患啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽可是兵糧中不可或缺之物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助 不是讓你小心慎言嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人 無妨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後再無需隱藏保密了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎 陣五郎 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的 朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.85,0:04:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您所言甚是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值此良機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.51,0:04:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就請伊賀眾看看我們練習的成果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可那舞是準備在婚儀中才展示的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當日展現更精彩的技藝便可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.15,0:04:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彫蟲小技 權充伊賀甲賀和解之賀禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹以此笛此舞 願世代永昌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非您每次與朧小姐相見都在練習這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那是什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我與朧小姐相見時會做何事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.25,0:05:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個 我可說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何問我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:34.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 請原諒丈助的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是甲賀最容易得意忘形的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不必介意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹也並不介懷的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 真是有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為甲賀人會更兇神惡煞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:07:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽了朧小姐講那些面相兇惡的伊賀眾的糗事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越來越有親近感了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您想聽多少我便說多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.55,0:07:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人若非親近相處便不能互相瞭解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 未見著在土岐嶺遇到的那幾位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來得有些晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.30,0:07:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然出言相邀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但終究還是難以接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.52,0:07:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 定非此等原因
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是無可奈何之事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚想必還有其他拒絕與我同席的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.31,0:07:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心 朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多花些時間 逐漸互相瞭解便可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們甲賀卍谷一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.28,0:08:04.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及你們伊賀鍔隱一族
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.10,0:08:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方各懷可怖的忍法秘技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.73,0:08:11.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因長年宿怨而互相憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之見實是愚蠢至極
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.09,0:08:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.24,0:08:21.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 你我攜手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬斷束縛兩族的鐵鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天地真正廣闊 讓風聲迴盪兩谷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.06,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.47,0:08:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已將丈助關進那間客屋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.50,0:08:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 卷軸的事切勿告訴他人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.33,0:08:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被朧小姐察覺便糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹 我們也出手試探一下如何
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:06.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天膳他們此刻應當取了將監性命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:09.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可天膳大人讓我等不可妄動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此更應有所行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.57,0:09:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 鵜殿丈助就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鐵板啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特意用這種牢房想困住本大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死我也
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒想到被朱絹討厭到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人傷心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:52.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:58.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別有居心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起那時的表情真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 為何垂下眼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.87,0:10:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是累了吧 夜也深了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回房休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.81,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並…並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉很紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.47,0:10:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何背對著我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人真壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說什麼 我沒聽清
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.54,0:10:50.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我對這樣的弦之介大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 果然還是去休息為好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個沒治的木頭人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之沒事便好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵜殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.25,0:11:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.26,0:11:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不顧羞恥前來相會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚宴上因為顧及伊賀眾人的眼光…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.89,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丈助…閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.55,0:11:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你走岔了真是抱歉 朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼逃離這房間的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個嘛 就是全憑滿腔愛念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難對付的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.64,0:11:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.17,0:11:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你的心意也與我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.01,0:12:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧來吧 朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.50,0:12:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就當一夜我的新娘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:19.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓人嘆服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.11,0:12:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來較量一下忍術吧 丈助閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若輸了就如你所願
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做一夜你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會留情哦 朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彼此彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.04,0:13:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請好好歇息 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:16.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.82,0:14:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 朱絹在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵜殿丈助 命喪於此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險好險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太無情了吧 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我若死了你要如何補償
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這死肉包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.69,0:15:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來勝負已分了 朱絹小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.54,0:15:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就按我們說好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.27,0:15:28.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.81,0:15:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朧小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.65,0:15:33.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵜殿大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.81,0:15:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底在這裏幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 真是太丟臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:47.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實是在下教而不改 又對朱絹小姐拉拉扯扯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於把她惹火了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請您對弦之介大人保密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.12,0:15:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知…知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.23,0:16:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 請莫要再做這樣的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下對敢國神社發誓
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.49,0:16:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs28\a6}敢國神社：位於三重縣上野市，祭神為伊賀的鼻祖敢國津命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知你是哪位 伊賀之人喲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.49,0:16:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支配爾等心靈、難以斷絕的憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.07,0:16:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其根深蒂固 方纔的晚宴上我已有切身體會
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望你們能斬斷陳年宿怨的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.22,0:16:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今應是我等攜手共書歷史新章之時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.24,0:16:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否相信我和朧小姐 助我們一臂之力？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱絹 無論鵜殿大人的玩笑有多過火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.22,0:17:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動用忍術還是有些過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.82,0:17:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.85,0:17:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是鹽倉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.97,0:17:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.35,0:17:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.19,0:17:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒 請您原諒 弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.76,0:17:45.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:51.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失…失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣五郎 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:57.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.90,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我下來 陣五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.49,0:18:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧…朧小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請…請莫要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陣五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…想刺殺弦之介大人是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 陣五郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…給我水
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.72,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朧小姐 如此下去陣五郎閣下會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.49,0:18:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准幫他 朱絹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.18,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…給我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.13,0:19:26.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方纔那殺氣 她是來真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.74,0:19:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…給我水 給我水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水 水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔細看看 這不是雨夜陣五郎閣下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:20:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你莫非是想以這副模樣刺殺弦之介大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:05.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我…水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 說吧 雨夜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今甲賀與伊賀即將和解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.95,0:20:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何還要殺弦之介大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水 給我水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你說 看 要多少水都有
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.93,0:20:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與服…服部家的…不戰之約解…解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 跟服部家的約定？然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即是說 伊賀與甲賀的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊賀與甲賀的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.43,0:21:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀與伊賀的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.29,0:21:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法之爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨 我是不會沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甲賀十人眾之一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鵜殿丈助 命喪於此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.24,0:23:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晨霧籠罩的甲賀村落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇氣自北方逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引領他們的是殘忍的邪念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰然老木所思為何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.52,0:23:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇襲 那是忍者的常用之道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卍谷的北之街頭
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.60,0:23:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今化為血之泥沼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.51,0:24:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 basilisk 甲賀忍法帖

